{"title_page": "8th Lux Style Awards", "text_new": "{{Infobox film awards\n| number              = 8\n| award               = Lux Style Awards\n| award_link          = Lux Style Awards\n| type                = \n| image               = \n| image_size = 200px\n| caption             = \n| date                = \n| site                = [[Karachi Expo Centre|Expo Centre]], [[Karachi]]\n| host                = \n| producer            = \n| director            = \n| organizer           = \n| best_picture        = \n| best_actor_film     = \n| best_actor          = \n| best_actress_film   = \n| best_actress        = \n| channel             = [[ARY Digital]]\n| network             = \n| duration            = \n| ratings             = \n| last                = 7th\n| next                = 9th\n}}\n\nThe 8th '''[[Lux Style Awards]]''' ceremony was held in [[Karachi Expo Centre|Expo Center]] in [[Karachi, Pakistan]]. The show was hosted by [[Ahsan Khan (actor)|Ahsan Khan]], [[Sana Nawaz]] and from the members of [[Banana News Network|BNN]]. Some of the film and music categories were removed from the award.<ref name=lux>{{cite web|title=Winners announced for 8th LUX Style Awards|url=http://www.fashioncentral.pk/people-parties/events/celebrations/story-383-winners-announced-for-8th-lux-style-awards/|publisher=fashioncentral.pk|accessdate=28 October 2013}}</ref> <ref name=awards>{{cite web|title=8th Lux Style Awards 2009|url=http://www.showbizpak.com/Lux2009.php#chitika_close_button|publisher=showbizpak.com|accessdate=28 October 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029200312/http://www.showbizpak.com/Lux2009.php#chitika_close_button|archive-date=29 October 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref> <ref name=blogspot>{{cite web|title=Lux Style Awards 2009|url=http://pkinnocentlover.blogspot.com/2009/06/lux-style-awards-2009.html|publisher=pkinnocentlover.blogspot.com|accessdate=28 October 2013}}</ref> <ref name=youtube>{{cite web|title=Lux Style Awards Red Carpet|url=https://www.